 +api prep. + loc.<BR>1 u, v<BR>2 у, в<BR>3 close by, in<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=026&d=FRI" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=fri&e=438" target="_blank">Correction</a>

