uttaratas<BR>1 nahoru, nalevo, na sever<BR>2 вверх, влево, на север<BR>3 above, to the left, northward<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=056&d=FRI" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=fri&e=1219" target="_blank">Correction</a>

उत्तरेण
uttareṇa<BR>1 nalevo od, na sever od<BR>2 влево от, на север от<BR>3 on the left side of, northward<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=056&d=FRI" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=fri&e=1220" target="_blank">Correction</a>

उत्तरण|उत्तरणं
uttaraṇa n.<BR>1 překročení, přechod<BR>2 переход<BR>3 crossing, passing over<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=056&d=FRI" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=fri&e=1221" target="_blank">Correction</a>

उत्तरसूक्त
uttarasūkta n.<BR>1 následující hymnus<BR>2 следующий гимн<BR>3 the following hymn<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=056&d=FRI" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=fri&e=1222" target="_blank">Correction</a>

