 +desid. vivikṣati<BR>1 chtíti vstoupiti<BR>2 желать вступить<BR>3 to wish to enter into<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=275&d=FRI" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=fri&e=6435" target="_blank">Correction</a>

